      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained in showroom-equivalent condition. This unit represents the pinnacle of its class, featuring a flawless exterior finish and an interior that remains indistinguishable from new. Every mechanical component has been rigorously inspected to ensure it meets our exacting standards for excellence. For the discerning collector or enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection, this offering is unparalleled in the current market.",
