    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting an impeccable 2018 Porsche 718 Cayman S, a true collector-grade specimen that has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled environment. The Guards Red exterior retains a deep, mirror-like luster, protected by a professional ceramic coating with absolutely zero stone chips or road rash. Inside, the Black leather interior remains in showroom state; the seat bolsters show no signs of entry wear, and the cabin still carries that distinct new-Porsche aroma. Every button, switch, and dial functions with tactile precision. Mechanically, this vehicle is beyond reproach, boasting a full Porsche dealership service history and having recently undergone a comprehensive multi-point inspection. With exceptionally low mileage and brand-new Michelin Pilot Sport 4S tires, this Cayman offers a driving experience indistinguishable from the day it left the factory. Included are both original keys, all owner manuals, and a thick binder of service documentation. This is a rare opportunity for the discerning enthusiast to acquire a modern classic in flawless condition.",
      "price": 43800.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
